      "command": "AICX_BENCH_ROWS=500000 AICX_BENCH_DIM=1024 cargo test -p aicx-retrieve --release --test mmap_adapter -- --ignored --nocapture profile_exact_scan_at_scale",
      "subject": "release-mode MmapDenseAdapter measured directly at the same isolated 500000 x 1024 scale and 6-project taxonomy, warm, cosine, top_k 10, 3 timed runs per mode",
